{
  "id": 87,
  "nameSimple": "Al-A'la",
  "nameArabic": "الأعلى",
  "versesCount": 19,
  "revelationPlace": "makkah",
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 5949,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "verseKey": "87:1",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": " سَبِّحِ ٱسْمَ رَبِّكَ ٱلْأَعْلَى",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102067,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Exalt the name of your Lord, the Most High,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752662,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你当赞颂你至高主的大名超绝万物，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5950,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "verseKey": "87:2",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ٱلَّذِى خَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102079,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Who created and proportioned",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752663,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他创造万物并使各物匀称。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5951,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "verseKey": "87:3",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَٱلَّذِى قَدَّرَ فَهَدَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102081,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And who destined and [then] guided",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752664,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他预定万物，而加以引导。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5952,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "verseKey": "87:4",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَٱلَّذِىٓ أَخْرَجَ ٱلْمَرْعَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102083,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And who brings out the pasture",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752665,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他生出牧草，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5953,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "verseKey": "87:5",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَجَعَلَهُۥ غُثَآءً أَحْوَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102085,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And [then] makes it black stubble.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752666,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "然后使它变成黑色的枯草。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5954,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "verseKey": "87:6",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "سَنُقْرِئُكَ فَلَا تَنسَىٰٓ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102086,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "We will make you recite, [O Muḥammad], and you will not forget,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752667,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我将使你诵读，故你不会忘记，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5955,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "verseKey": "87:7",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِلَّا مَا شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ ۚ إِنَّهُۥ يَعْلَمُ ٱلْجَهْرَ وَمَا يَخْفَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102087,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Except what Allāh should will. Indeed, He knows what is declared and what is hidden.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752668,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "除非安拉所欲忘记的。他的确知道显著的和隐微的言行。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5956,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "verseKey": "87:8",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَنُيَسِّرُكَ لِلْيُسْرَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102088,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And We will ease you toward ease.<sup foot_note=230386>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752669,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我将使你遵循平易的道路，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5957,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "verseKey": "87:9",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَذَكِّرْ إِن نَّفَعَتِ ٱلذِّكْرَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102089,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "So remind, if the reminder should benefit;<sup foot_note=230387>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752670,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "故你当教诲众人，如果教诲有裨于他们的话。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5958,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "verseKey": "87:10",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "سَيَذَّكَّرُ مَن يَخْشَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102068,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "He who fears [Allāh] will be reminded.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752671,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "畏主的人，将觉悟；",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5959,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "verseKey": "87:11",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَيَتَجَنَّبُهَا ٱلْأَشْقَى",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102069,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "But the wretched one will avoid it –",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752672,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "薄命的人，将退避，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5960,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "verseKey": "87:12",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ٱلَّذِى يَصْلَى ٱلنَّارَ ٱلْكُبْرَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102070,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[He] who will [enter and] burn in the greatest Fire,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752673,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他将入于大火，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5961,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "verseKey": "87:13",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ثُمَّ لَا يَمُوتُ فِيهَا وَلَا يَحْيَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102071,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Neither dying therein nor living.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752674,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "然后，在火里不死也不活。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5962,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "verseKey": "87:14",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "قَدْ أَفْلَحَ مَن تَزَكَّىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102072,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "He has certainly succeeded who purifies himself",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752675,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "纯洁者必定成功，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5963,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "verseKey": "87:15",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَذَكَرَ ٱسْمَ رَبِّهِۦ فَصَلَّىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102073,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And mentions the name of his Lord and prays.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752676,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他记念他的主的尊名，而谨守拜功。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5964,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "verseKey": "87:16",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "بَلْ تُؤْثِرُونَ ٱلْحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنْيَا",
      "pageNumber": 592,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102074,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "But you prefer the worldly life,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752677,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "不然，你们却选择今世的生活；",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5965,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "verseKey": "87:17",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَٱلْـَٔاخِرَةُ خَيْرٌ وَأَبْقَىٰٓ",
      "pageNumber": 592,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102075,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "While the Hereafter is better and more enduring.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752678,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "其实，后世是更好的，是更长久的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5966,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "verseKey": "87:18",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّ هَـٰذَا لَفِى ٱلصُّحُفِ ٱلْأُولَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 592,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102076,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, this is in the former scriptures,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752679,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "这确是载在古经典中的，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5967,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "verseKey": "87:19",
      "hizbNumber": 60,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 237,
      "rukuNumber": 531,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "صُحُفِ إِبْرَٰهِيمَ وَمُوسَىٰ",
      "pageNumber": 592,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102077,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "The scriptures of Abraham and Moses.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752680,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "载在易卜拉欣和穆萨的经典中的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}